name: FATS Digital
overview: FATS Digital is Australia’s largest media duplication and replication service provider with locations in Melbourne, Sydney, Brisbane and Canberra. Specialising in DVD, CD and Blu-Ray duplication, replication and authoring, FATS digital operates from ISO9002 accredited facilities. FATS Digital provides a complete digital service encompassing blank media & equipment hire to duplication and replication services along with graphic design, packaging and order fulfilment. The company also assists with video file transfers and USB and Flash memory design & duplication. FATS Digital was established in 1986 and its expansion is a testament to its trusted partner status with scores of businesses across Australia for quality digital services.
